Summary:
Nano Banana Pro has been released by Google and it completely dominates every other AI image editor and AI text to image model across many use cases. The ability to create infographics and extensive text is particularly mind-blowing. Nano Banana Pro is powered by Gemini 3 giving it the ability to think through prompts and use search before generating. It is miles beyond many of the other image models. I cover tons of use cases and challenges.
